        "text": "δὲ αὐτοῖς",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), because in that year the joint labours of Paul and Barnabas occasioned so considerable an enlargement of the church, and therewith naturally its increase in social and public consideration. And it was at Antioch that this name was borne ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
